<script type="text/javascript">podPressShowHidePlayer('1', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2010/1-10/epi-00364-follow-up-22-vs-shotgun.mp3', 290, 24, 'false', 'http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress//images/vpreview_center.png', 'Episode-364- Follow Up on the 22 vs. the Shotgun', 'The Survival Podcast');</script><p>Today&#8217;s show is a follow up on <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/22-rifle-vs-the-shotgun-for-survival-needs" target="_blank">Episode 360</a> so the show notes and links will be quite brief.  We are going to discuss your comments, objections and thoughts on the 22 vs. the <a title="Shotgun" href="http://tspwiki.com/index.php?title=Shotgun">Shotgun</a> for survival needs.</p>
<p><span style="color: #800000;"><strong>Join me today as we discuss&#8230;</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Why even debate a one <a target="_blank" title="gun" href="http://tspwiki.com/index.php?title=Firearm">gun</a> solution</li>
<li>What about the 22 Hornet</li>
<li>What about the 44 Magnum</li>
<li>What about the 22 Magnum</li>
<li>What limitations do certain actions have</li>
<li>What can we do to reduce noise beyond even the 22 low report</li>
<li>What about break down weapons like the AR7</li>
<li>And more!</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="color: #800000;"><strong>Resources for today’s show…</strong></span></p>
