			<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/56f94b9b3e745104d19c3b9d474f20c8?s=48&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />
			<cite class="fn">Reluctant Lemming</cite>

